Package: HMM
Type: Package
Title: Hidden Markov Models
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Marco Floess
Maintainer: <mfloess@outlook.de>
Description: Framework for creating Hidden Markov Models,
  generating observation sequences from given models,
  computing the probability of a given observation sequence for a model,
  computing the most likely underlying state sequences for a given observation sequence for a model,
  estimating the model parameters given a set of observation sequences.
